                  <h3 class="content-text">Analysing performance of nuclear reactor's instrumentaion - Bhabha Atomic Research Center (BARC)</h3>
                  <ul style="list-style: none;">
                     <li>Analysed instrumentation required in nuclear reactors, researched on extremely low current driving capabilities of op-amp amplifiers and development of such models. Analysed Mock Instrumentation Circuits: Sorted and Hacked in effort to come out with what an unknown circuit did.
                     </li>
                  </ul>
